  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348060/extras/ed24d54b1e7e6590f45bea7f6fd5b615.avif?t=1670242824\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>Bug Blast is a top-down space shooter that provides the player multiple ways of carrying out the stand against the hive of alien space bugs that are invading our<br>solar system. The player travels the solar system recovering fallen stations from the war.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348060/extras/a40fc13b180859695c853dd6bb194d1f.avif?t=1670242824\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 unique weapon types<br></li><li>3 distict, challenging enemies<br></li><li>Objective-based Gameplay<br></li><li>Difficulty Scaling<br></li><li>Engaging Boss<br></li><li>Arcade-like Controls</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348060/extras/a0314dc9cb71f37107ea1d9189626940.avif?t=1670242824\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>This game was developed as a student project at DigiPen Institute of Technology and was created for educational purposes only. Please check out our publisher page for more information.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348060/extras/ed24d54b1e7e6590f45bea7f6fd5b615.avif?t=1670242824\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>Bug Blast is a top-down space shooter that provides the player multiple ways of carrying out the stand against the hive of alien space bugs that are invading our<br>solar system. The player travels the solar system recovering fallen stations from the war.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348060/extras/a40fc13b180859695c853dd6bb194d1f.avif?t=1670242824\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 unique weapon types<br></li><li>3 distict, challenging enemies<br></li><li>Objective-based Gameplay<br></li><li>Difficulty Scaling<br></li><li>Engaging Boss<br></li><li>Arcade-like Controls</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1348060/extras/a0314dc9cb71f37107ea1d9189626940.avif?t=1670242824\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>This game was developed as a student project at DigiPen Institute of Technology and was created for educational purposes only. Please check out our publisher page for more information.",
